The,GitHub,Issue,Labels,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,the,GitHub,labeling,service,into,their,applications,enabling,functions,i,e,listing,labels,for,repositories,creating,updating,deleting,single,label,and,listing,adding,removing,replacing,labels,for,issues,This,API,requires,two,factor,authentication,GitHub,is,one,of,the,software,providers,that,specialize,in,a,wide,range,of,application,development